&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payroll &amp;amp; People Systems:&lt;/strong&gt; Administer payroll processes in partnership with Finance, and maintain and optimize our HR systems, identifying opportunities to streamline and automate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employee Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as a go-to resource for employee questions, managing our ticketing system through Jira and meeting defined SLAs.&lt;/li&gt;
