&lt;p&gt;The Inspections team is responsible for one of Hover&#39;s fastest-growing products and plays a critical role in helping some of the largest insurers in the world make better decisions about properties. We&#39;re looking for a Senior Software Engineer who can help us scale that product while shaping its future architecture. You&#39;ll begin by building customer-facing features that improve the inspection experience and quickly grow into helping lead a strategic evolution of the platform as we transition portions of our React Native application into native SDK capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who enjoys balancing product thinking with technical depth. You&#39;ll work closely with Product, Design, QA, and Engineering partners to solve real customer problems, improve platform reliability, and influence decisions that will impact both Hover&#39;s applications and future external SDK consumers. If you&#39;re excited about product ownership, working with ambiguity, and the opportunity to help define the next generation of a rapidly growing product, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
