&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll play a key role in the evolution of Hover Inspections, leading initiatives that improve platform reliability, scalability, and developer experience while helping define the future architecture of the product. As we continue investing in our mobile platform and SDK strategy, you&#39;ll evaluate technical tradeoffs, influence architectural decisions, and help establish a foundation that supports long-term growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beyond delivering features, you&#39;ll contribute to engineering excellence across the team through thoughtful system design, strong testing practices, code reviews, and operational improvements. You&#39;ll help raise the bar for quality while enabling the team to move quickly and confidently in service of our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most importantly, you&#39;ll operate with a high degree of ownership. Taking projects from idea to implementation, launch, and ongoing support while helping build products that are reliable, scalable, and valuable in the real-world environments where our customers work every day.&lt;/p&gt;
