&lt;p&gt;The insurance claims process is one of the most complex, high-stakes workflows in the real world — and it&#39;s still largely broken. Adjusters are making damage assessments from photos taken on a smartphone. Carriers are paying for estimates built on guesswork. And homeowners are waiting weeks or months for outcomes that should take hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hover is changing that. Our 3D scan and AI platform is already embedded in the claims workflows of nine out of the ten top insurance carriers, and we&#39;re just getting started. We&#39;re hiring a Staff&amp;nbsp;PM to help own and define our next chapter in claims — across the workflows that matter most to carriers, adjusters, and the homeowners they serve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role spans the full range: some of it is 0-to-1, defining new product territory; some of it is block-and-tackle, making existing enterprise workflows faster and better. Both matter. You&#39;ll be shaping what the product becomes, not inheriting a finished roadmap. You&#39;ll work directly with enterprise customers to co-build solutions, partner with engineering and CV/ML leadership to define what&#39;s technically possible, and help Hover become the standard for AI-powered claims.&lt;/p&gt;
